import React from 'react' import JsonData from '../contract.json' import "./CSS/Table.css" function JsonDataDisplay(){ const DisplayData=JsonData.map( (info)=>{ return( {info.id} {info.company_id} {info.contract_name} {info.contract_length} {info.contract_value} {info.description} {info.progamming_language} {info.location} {info.open} {info.date} ) } ) return (
{DisplayData}
ID ComID ConName ConLen ConVal ConDes ProLan Loc Open Date
) } export default JsonDataDisplay;
